message: /* Please add me to the Free Guy (movie) Cast list. */
/* Please add me to the Free Guy (movie) Cast list.  */ new section

Added myself (Mark Lainer) as Hostage (AKA "Hands Up Guy) one of the NPCs with dialogue in Free Guy. I am a SAG-AFTRA Principal in the film and was used as a meme and character in promotions on Twitter and Instagram by Twentieth Century)
Added myself (Mark Lainer) as Hostage (AKA "Hands Up Guy) one of the NPCs with dialogue in Free Guy.
I am in the film in a principal role (https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6264654/fullcredits) and added myself.

Added back Mark Lainer as Hostage. Actor had dialogue and was a SAG Principal. Actor was one of the main NPCs with dialogue, alongside Britne Oldford, Camille Kostek and Mike Devine.
